r />\n黑警已經該意唔帶證去打你地！ （有朋友做輔警講）<br />\n連我藍絲爸爸都話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(佢地條氣唔順囉 困住你地就係想打鍋你地之後拉你！）<br />\n<br />\n咁我想問覺得我地過份既.巴絲打！？<br />\n係唔係要見到我地既手足.<br />\n要比人打到頭破血流.殘廢甚至死亡！<br />\n你先會叫我地還手啦！<br />\n<br />\n我地當初既承諾！<br />\n兄弟爬山.各有各做！<br />\n不割蓆.不分化.不指責去左邊？<br />\n<br />\n幾位烈士 留低既信息！你地又忘記左？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:31:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89bb155851314cdbe8b1de4d27e35e68736ed230","tid":1321832,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2d545c8cb2f323b33b369b30932a1fd4d31c435","tid":1321832,"uid":280150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c7433831646e3f38307f9e98d9736fbac474379","tid":1321832,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"657573d51de139ee05ae909615e17c4bddbc5380","tid":1321832,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:18:54.000Z","msg":"同夢<br />\n琴晚發左個刻骨銘心既夢，想同大家分享一下<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djqmQS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djqmQS</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:26:47.000Z","msg":"你夢見既同我一模一樣！<br />\n真係好真實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82450d0f8cd1ba2070b47c9a6f24720517b3da0","tid":1321832,"uid":280150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:36:15.000Z","msg":"我發呢個post 唔係想分化！ 只係想諗敵人可憐之前<br />\n有無諗過唔還手既後果？"},{"pid":"345a54e7bb629d32677684d885eae9ba3cb8ab27","tid":1321832,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:39:48.000Z","msg":"係打手偽命題，七一都無逆轉，點解沙田會逆轉？乜警察比玻璃重要咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkg